            <div class="grid">
                <div class="skills-group">
                    <span class="label">Technical Skills:</span> Python, Lua, JavaScript, REST API Design, WebSocket Programming, Discord API, Roblox Studio, Git, TinyDB, Reverse Engineering, Security Analysis, Server Performance Optimization, Debugging, Automation.
                </div>
                <div class="skills-group">
                    <span class="label">Development:</span> Full-stack Game Development, Bot Development, API Wrapper Design, Modular Architecture, Client-Server Systems, Live Operations Management.
