                </span>
            </h2>
            <div class="grid">

            <div class="entry">
                <div class="entry-title-line">
                    <a class="entry-name" href="https://github.com/stafawashere/Allusion" target="_blank">Allusion</a>
                    <span class="entry-separator"> &mdash; </span>
